column5: The time has finally come.    HARD WATER SEASON   I got a bag of these baits ,and can not wait til the morning to give them a go. Slammers/swammers,look out.  No disrespect to my friend Mark kulick. All in fun.  Read the fine print,as they say.   And no,you can not know the maker or brand right now.
Try those in March after the fish have been hassled, then you'll know if they work or not    Early season lakers will eat rope, lol!     Good luck tomorrow, I'd be out but I'm oncall.
Me too,but I left my cell at home.LOL
I like the way you think  :)
Hell I,ll try them in May on calm waters,but for some reason,I dont think we,ll be stopping for a chance.  Fish on
We'll be out. I'll shoot ya a text.  good luck, Ry
